
## HAZARD WARNING SWITCH INSPECTION  


1. Remove the hazard warning switch. (Refer to 09-18 HAZARD WARNING SWITCH REMOVAL/INSTALLATION.) 
2. Inspect for continuity between the hazard warning switch terminals by using an ohmmeter.  

![](images/0.jpg)
  

![](images/1.jpg)
  

![](images/2.jpg)
  


3. If not as specified, replace the hazard warning switch.  


